 the resolved 5.0.1 stack uses Netty 4.2.2.Final, which needs explicit Unsafe-related system properties for Java 25 native-image runs.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"For native-image runtime tests on JDK 25, ensure the generated test/build setup passes `-Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow` and `-Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true` to the native test runtime, not only for 5.0.0 but also for 5.0.1. Use a local Vert.x `HttpServer` bound to `127.0.0.1`/port `0` for WebClient requests instead of relying on external network services.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Local Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative; the issue may still require metadata fixes if these system properties are present and the native run still fails.\",\n    \"Optional Vert.x modules such as `vertx-auth-oauth2` are declared optional and should not be added unless the generated tests intentionally cover OAuth2-specific APIs.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0692732fd5ef4056016a405790d40c8193823916062d62404f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1861, "output": 797, "cacheRead": 27136, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 29794, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782601607669, "responseId": "resp_0692732fd5ef4056016a4057884250819394900a6b77825169"}, "toolResults": []}
